<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head')  %> 
    <style>
        .topic-card {
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .topic-card:hover {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .avatar {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
    </style>

    <!-- Include the timeLapse.js file -->
    <script src="/timeLapse.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/nav')  %>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
            <ol class="breadcrumb">
                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Forum</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Computer Science</li>
            </ol>
        </nav>

        <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <h1 class="mb-0">Computer Science</h1>
                <p class="lead">Discuss all things related to computer science, from programming languages to algorithms and beyond.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-md-end">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#newTopicModal">
                    <i class="bi bi-plus-circle"></i> New Topic
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-9">
                <div class="card mb-4">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <ul class="nav nav-tabs card-header-tabs">
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link active" href="#">Latest Topics</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="#">Most Viewed</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="#">Hot Discussions</a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="list-group">
                            <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action topic-card">
                                <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
                                    <h5 class="mb-1">Best practices for learning Data Structures and Algorithms</h5>
                                    <small class="text-muted">3 days ago</small>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-1">I'm struggling with understanding complex data structures. Any tips or resources that helped you master DSA?</p>
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-2">
                                    <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=32&width=32" alt="JohnDoe" class="avatar me-2">
                                    <small class="text-muted">
                                        Posted by JohnDoe
                                        <i class="bi bi-chat-dots ms-2"></i> 15 comments
                                        <i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up ms-2"></i> 23 likes
                                    </small>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action topic-card">
                                <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
                                    <h5 class="mb-1">Comparing Python vs Java for backend development</h5>
                                    <small class="text-muted">1 week ago</small>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-1">I'm starting a new project and can't decide between Python and Java for the backend. What are the pros and cons of each in 2023?</p>
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-2">
                                    <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=32&width=32" alt="BackendDev" class="avatar me-2">
                                    <small class="text-muted">
                                        Posted by BackendDev
                                        <i class="bi bi-chat-dots ms-2"></i> 32 comments
                                        <i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up ms-2"></i> 45 likes
                                    </small>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action topic-card">
                                <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
                                    <h5 class="mb-1">How to prepare for technical interviews at FAANG companies?</h5>
                                    <small class="text-muted">2 weeks ago</small>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-1">I have interviews coming up with big tech companies. What's the best way to prepare for their coding challenges and system design questions?</p>
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-2">
                                    <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=32&width=32" alt="FutureEngineer" class="avatar me-2">
                                    <small class="text-muted">
                                        Posted by FutureEngineer
                                        <i class="bi bi-chat-dots ms-2"></i> 28 comments
                                        <i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up ms-2"></i> 56 likes
                                    </small>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <nav aria-label="Topics pagination">
                    <ul class="pagination justify-content-center">
                        <li class="page-item disabled">
                            <a class="page-link" href="#" tabindex="-1" aria-disabled="true">Previous</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="page-item active" aria-current="page">
                            <a class="page-link" href="#">1</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#">2</a></li>
                        <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#">3</a></li>
                        <li class="page-item">
                            <a class="page-link" href="#">Next</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="card mb-4">
                    <div class="card-header">Category Stats</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p><i class="bi bi-file-text"></i> Total Topics: 1,234</p>
                        <p><i class="bi bi-chat"></i> Total Posts: 5,678</p>
                        <p><i class="bi bi-person"></i> Active Users: 789</p>
                        <p><i class="bi bi-eye"></i> Total Views: 98,765</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card mb-4">
                    <div class="card-header">Top Contributors</div>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                            <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=32&width=32" alt="User1" class="avatar me-2">
                            <span>CodeMaster</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-primary ms-auto">152 posts</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                            <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=32&width=32" alt="User2" class="avatar me-2">
                            <span>AlgorithmPro</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-primary ms-auto">98 posts</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                            <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=32&width=32" alt="User3" class="avatar me-2">
                            <span>DataWizard</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-primary ms-auto">87 posts</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">Related Categories</div>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                        <li class="list-group-item"><a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Web Development</a></li>
                        <li class="list-group-item"><a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Artificial Intelligence</a></li>
                        <li class="list-group-item"><a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Data Science</a></li>
                        <li class="list-group-item"><a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Cybersecurity</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- New Topic Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="newTopicModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="newTopicModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="newTopicModalLabel">Create New Topic in Computer Science</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <form>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="topicTitle" class="form-label">Title</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="topicTitle" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="topicContent" class="form-label">Content</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="topicContent" rows="5" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="topicTags" class="form-label">Tags</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="topicTags" placeholder="Separate tags with commas">
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Create Topic</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer')  %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>